---
// Testimonials.astro — Lo que dicen quienes ya trabajaron conmigo
// Hardcodeado por ahora. Los testimonios son reales de clientes.
---

<section id="testimonios" data-reveal class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Fondo decorativo sutil -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_rgba(251,191,36,0.04)_0%,_transparent_60%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom_left,_rgba(251,191,36,0.03)_0%,_transparent_50%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-3">Testimonios</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
        Lo que dicen <span class="text-amber-400">mis clientes</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto mt-4 text-lg">
        No confíes en mi palabra. Esto es lo que opinan quienes ya confiaron en mí.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de testimonios -->
    <div data-reveal-stagger class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-zinc-900/80 hover:border-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-500">
        <!-- Comillas decorativas -->
        <svg class="absolute top-4 right-6 text-amber-500/10 w-12 h-12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151C7.546 6.068 5.983 8.789 5.983 11H10v10H0z"/>
        </svg>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10">
          "Hernán transformó por completo nuestra presencia online. Pasamos de tener una web que no funcionaba a una plataforma que nos genera clientes cada semana. Profesional total."
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-sm shrink-0">
            CM
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Carlos Martínez</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Dueño — Café Mi Tierra</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-auto flex gap-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
